  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released\u00a010/13/2017 CT 11:04 AM CT (16:04 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.7-NewBusinessIntelligenceFeatures\">New Business Intelligence Features</h2><p><strong>Table calculations!\u00a0</strong></p><p>Table calculations give you the\u00a0ability to run calculations on datasets.</p><p><strong>New Automator delivery options</strong></p><p>You now have the ability to automate data delivery via email, SFTP, Webhooks, or to an S3 bucket.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.7-LoginPageUpdates\">Login Page Updates</h2><p>We added some new styles to the login page, no functional changes here.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.7-EditingStaffRoles\">Editing Staff Roles</h2><p>We have had reports of some intermittent issues with saving staff roles, where roles would disappear when updates were made. These issues have been resolved.\u00a0</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.7-CustomerBalanceAdjustmentNotes\">Customer Balance Adjustment\u00a0Notes</h2><p>Customer credit notes are now\u00a0shown in the credit transaction history, as expected : )</p><p />",
